tafsir[3]{c,v,t}:
  20,3,"We only revealed it to be a reminder for those whom Allah has blessed so that they fear Him."
  20,10,"When he saw a fire whilst travelling and he said to his family: Stay here––I can see a fire. Maybe I can bring you a flaming brand from it or find somebody to guide me to the path."
  20,12,"I am your Lord. Take off your shoes in preparation for your conversation with me. You are in the purified valley (of Tuwa.)"